    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed and six remain as epistemic gaps. Achieved levels are below required levels across all assessed factors; however, compensating engineering controls and conservative safety margins applied to the hemolysis threshold are judged sufficient to support regulatory submission at this stage. The package is accepted pending resolution of model form and input uncertainty gaps in the next assessment cycle.",
